text: Rohit Sardana left us too soon. Full of energy, passionate about India’s progress and a kind hearted soul, Rohit will be missed by many people. His untimely demise has left a huge void in the media world. Condolences to his family, friends and admirers. Om Shanti.

text:

https://t.co/vzl6ahY1O2

description: Prime Minister of India
text: आप सभी को होली की ढेर सारी शुभकामनाएं। आनंद, उमंग, हर्ष और उल्लास का यह त्योहार हर किसी के जीवन में नए जोश और नई ऊर्जा का संचार करे।

description: Prime Minister of India
text: रामनवमी की मंगलकामनाएं। देशवासियों पर भगवान श्रीराम की असीम अनुकंपा सदा बनी रहे। जय श्रीराम!

description: Prime Minister of India
text: हनुमान जयंती का पावन अवसर भगवान हनुमान की करुणा और समर्पण भाव को याद करने का दिन है। मेरी कामना है कि कोरोना महामारी के खिलाफ जारी लड़ाई में निरंतर उनका आशीर्वाद प्राप्त होता रहे। साथ ही उनके जीवन और आदर्शों से हमेशा प्रेरणा मिलती रहे।

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Congratulations to Mamata Didi for @AITCofficial's win in West Bengal. The Centre will continue to extend all possible support to the West Bengal Government to fulfil people’s aspirations and also to overcome the COVID-19 pandemic. @MamataOfficial

description: Prime Minister of India
text: I pray for the good health and quick recovery of Lok Sabha MP Shri @RahulGandhi Ji.

description: Prime Minister of India
text:
Today’s record-breaking vaccination numbers are gladdening. The vaccine remains our strongest weapon to fight COVID-19. Congratulations to those who got vaccinated and kudos to all the front-line warriors working hard to ensure so many citizens got the vaccine. 

Well done India!

description: Prime Minister of India
text: In the passing away of Shri Milkha Singh Ji, we have lost a colossal sportsperson, who captured the nation’s imagination and had a special place in the hearts of countless Indians. His inspiring personality endeared himself to millions. Anguished by his passing away. https://t.co/h99RNbXI28

description: Prime Minister of India
text: सभी देशवासियों को नव संवत्सर की मंगलकामनाएं। यह पावन अवसर हर किसी के जीवन में हर्षोल्लास लेकर आए।

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Tomorrow, will be chairing high-level meetings to review the prevailing COVID-19 situation. Due to that, I would not be going to West Bengal.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: अपने अप्रतिम साहस, शौर्य और युद्ध कौशल से मां भारती को गौरवान्वित करने वाले महान योद्धा महाराणा प्रताप को उनकी जयंती पर आदरपूर्ण श्रद्धांजलि। मातृभूमि के लिए उनका त्याग और समर्पण सदैव स्मरणीय रहेगा।

description: Prime Minister of India
text: I congratulate all the colleagues who have taken oath today and wish them the very best for their ministerial tenure. We will continue working to fulfil aspirations of the people and build a strong and prosperous India. #Govt4Growth https://t.co/AVz9vL77bO

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Wishing our former Prime Minister, Dr. Manmohan Singh Ji good health and a speedy recovery.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Congratulations to Mamata Didi on taking oath as West Bengal’s Chief Minister. @MamataOfficial

description: Prime Minister of India
text:
Got my second dose of the COVID-19 vaccine at AIIMS today.

Vaccination is among the few ways we have, to defeat the virus.

If you are eligible for the vaccine, get your shot soon. Register on https://t.co/hXdLpmaYSP. https://t.co/XZzv6ULdan

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Glimpses from the Zen Garden inaugurated today at AMA, Ahmedabad. https://t.co/b4CaE5rFeK

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Prayed at the Madurai Meenakshi Amman Temple. https://t.co/ZUDRIZavDH

description: Prime Minister of India
text: I would like to thank my sisters and brothers of West Bengal who have blessed our party. From a negligible presence earlier, BJP’s presence has significantly increased. BJP will keep serving the people. I applaud each and every Karyakarta for their spirited effort in the polls.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: I thank the people of Karnataka, Maharashtra, Gujarat, Rajasthan and Uttarakhand for blessing the BJP in various by-polls. Our party will keep working for people’s welfare. Gratitude to the BJP Karyakartas for their untiring determination.

description: Prime Minister of India
text:
Popular across generations, a body of work few can boast of, diverse roles and an endearing personality...that’s Shri @rajinikanth Ji for you. 

It is a matter of immense joy that Thalaiva has been conferred with the Dadasaheb Phalke Award. Congratulations to him.

description: Prime Minister of India
text:
Prayed at Gurudwara Sis Ganj Sahib today. 

We can never forget the life, ideals and supreme sacrifice of Sri Guru Teg Bahadur Ji. https://t.co/62teTxLJsp

description: Prime Minister of India
text: On the way to the rally in Kanyakumari, caught a glimpse of the majestic Vivekananda Rock Memorial and the grand Thiruvalluvar Statue. https://t.co/Mveo5k1pTa

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Dilip Kumar Ji will be remembered as a cinematic legend. He was blessed with unparalleled brilliance, due to which audiences across generations were enthralled. His passing away is a loss to our cultural world. Condolences to his family, friends and innumerable admirers. RIP.

description: Prime Minister of India
text:
यूपी जिला पंचायत चुनाव में भाजपा की शानदार विजय विकास, जनसेवा और कानून के राज के लिए जनता जनार्दन का दिया हुआ आशीर्वाद है।
इसका श्रेय मुख्यमंत्री योगी जी की नीतियों और पार्टी कार्यकर्ताओं के अथक परिश्रम को जाता है। यूपी सरकार और भाजपा संगठन को इसके लिए हार्दिक बधाई।

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Congratulations to Thiru @mkstalin on being sworn-in as Tamil Nadu Chief Minister.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Greetings to everyone on the special occasion of the Rath Yatra. We bow to Lord Jagannath and pray that his blessings bring good health and prosperity in everyone’s lives. Jai Jagannath!

description: Prime Minister of India
text: International Nurses Day is a day to express gratitude to the hardworking nursing staff, who is at the forefront of fighting COVID-19. Their sense of duty, compassion and commitment towards a healthy India is exemplary.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Met the Leader of the Opposition in the West Bengal Assembly, Shri Suvendu Adhikari. @SuvenduWB https://t.co/HJXsOKxk1h

description: Prime Minister of India
text: As you complete your successful tenure as the Prime Minister of the State of Israel, I convey my profound gratitude for your leadership and personal attention to India-Israel strategic partnership @netanyahu.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: अपनी समृद्ध संस्कृति और वैभवशाली विरासत के लिए विख्यात राजस्थान के सभी भाइयों और बहनों को राजस्थान दिवस की बहुत-बहुत शुभकामनाएं।

description: Prime Minister of India
text:
Eid Mubarak! 

Best wishes on Eid-ul-Adha. May this day further the spirit of collective empathy, harmony and inclusivity in the service of greater good.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: The untimely demise of noted actor Vivek has left many saddened. His comic timing and intelligent dialogues entertained people. Both in his films and his life, his concern for the environment and society shone through. Condolences to his family, friends and admirers. Om Shanti.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Whenever you get the opportunity, do visit Jammu and Kashmir and witness the scenic Tulip festival. In addition to the tulips, you will experience the warm hospitality of the people of Jammu and Kashmir. https://t.co/RuZorHWBrO

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Congratulations to @himantabiswa Ji and the other Ministers who took oath today. I am confident this team will add momentum to the development journey of Assam and fulfil aspirations of the people.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Pained by the loss of lives due to a fire at a hospital in Bharuch. Condolences to the bereaved families.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Feeling blessed after praying at the Jeshoreshwari Kali Temple. https://t.co/8CzSSXt9PS

description: Prime Minister of India
text: 1 lakh portable oxygen concentrators will be procured, 500 more PSA oxygen plants sanctioned from PM-CARES. This will improve access to oxygen, specially in district HQs and Tier-2 cities. https://t.co/oURX74RYt1

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Spoke on phone to His Holiness the @DalaiLama to convey greetings on his 86th birthday. We wish him a long and healthy life.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Praying for the good health and fast recovery of Rajasthan CM Shri @ashokgehlot51 Ji and his wife, Smt. Sunita Ji.

description: Prime Minister of India
text:
Oxygen plants in every district to ensure adequate oxygen availability...

An important decision that will boost oxygen availability to hospitals and help people across the nation. https://t.co/GnbtjyZzWT

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Best wishes to the people of Telangana on the state’s Formation Day. The state is blessed with a unique culture and hardworking people who have excelled in many areas. Praying for the good health and well-being of the people of Telangana.

description: Prime Minister of India
text:
Supporting our nation’s future!

Several children lost their parents due to COVID-19. The Government will care for these children, ensure a life of dignity & opportunity for them. PM-CARES for Children will ensure education & other assistance to children. https://t.co/V3LsG3wcus

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Spoke to my dear friend President @EmmanuelMacron. I thanked him for France’s prompt assistance to India’s COVID-19 response. We also discussed bilateral, regional and global issues, including cooperation in climate action and Indo-Pacific.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Had a fruitful conversation with @POTUS @JoeBiden today. We discussed the evolving COVID situation in both countries in detail. I thanked President Biden for the support being provided by the United States to India.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Landed in Dhaka. I thank PM Sheikh Hasina for the special welcome at the airport. This visit will contribute to even stronger bilateral relations between our nations. https://t.co/oWFydFH2BG

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Last phase of the 2021 West Bengal elections takes place today. In line with the COVID-19 protocols, I call upon people to cast their vote and enrich the festival of democracy.

description: Prime Minister of India
text:
The #DarkDaysOfEmergency can never be forgotten. The period from 1975 to 1977 witnessed a systematic destruction of institutions. 

Let us pledge to do everything possible to strengthen India’s democratic spirit, and live up to the values enshrined in our Constitution.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Through PM-CARES, 1.5 lakh units of Oxycare Systems will be procured. This is a system developed by DRDO and has several benefits. https://t.co/xYUcqUxtGX

description: Prime Minister of India
text: I would like to congratulate Shri N.Rangasamy Ji on taking oath as Puducherry CM. Best wishes for the tenure ahead.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Thank you Thiruvananthapuram! https://t.co/zog7lVUXsE

description: Prime Minister of India
text:
देश के करोड़ों अन्नदाताओं के लिए कल का दिन बेहद महत्वपूर्ण है। सुबह 11 बजे वीडियो कॉन्फ्रेंसिंग के जरिए प्रधानमंत्री किसान सम्मान निधि की 8वीं किस्त जारी करने का सौभाग्य प्राप्त होगा। इस अवसर पर अपने किसान भाई-बहनों के साथ संवाद भी करूंगा।
https://t.co/QKUL2SFO7e

description: Prime Minister of India
text: You left us too soon, Sunil Jain. I will miss reading your columns and hearing your frank as well as insightful views on diverse matters. You leave behind an inspiring range of work. Journalism is poorer today, with your sad demise. Condolences to family and friends. Om Shanti.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: भगवान महावीर का जीवन संदेश हमें शांति और आत्मसंयम की सीख देता है। जब हम सभी देशवासी मिलकर कोरोना के इस संकट का मुकाबला कर रहे हैं, ऐसे समय में महावीर जयंती पर मेरी भगवान महावीर से प्रार्थना है कि सभी को स्वस्थ रखें और हमारे प्रयासों को सफलता का आशीर्वाद दें।

text: The seventh phase of the West Bengal elections takes place today. Urging people to exercise their franchise and follow all COVID-19 related protocols.

description: Prime Minister of India

सरकार किसानों के जीवन को बेहतर बनाने के लिए प्रतिबद्ध है। इसलिए अंतरराष्ट्रीय मूल्यों में बढ़ोतरी के बावजूद हमने उन्हें पुरानी दरों पर ही खाद मुहैया कराने का निर्णय लिया है। आज के फैसले के बाद DAP खाद का एक बैग 2400 रु की जगह 1200 रु में ही मिलेगा।

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Today is the birth anniversary of my friend, late Ram Vilas Paswan Ji. I miss his presence greatly.  He was one of India’s most experienced Parliamentarians and administrators. His contributions to public service and empowering the downtrodden will always be remembered.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: गुरु पूर्णिमा के पावन अवसर पर देशवासियों को हार्दिक बधाई।

description: Prime Minister of India
text: गीता प्रेस के अध्यक्ष और सनातन साहित्य को जन-जन तक पहुंचाने वाले राधेश्याम खेमका जी के निधन से अत्यंत दुख हुआ है। खेमका जी जीवनपर्यंत विभिन्न सामाजिक कार्यों में सक्रिय रहे। शोक की इस घड़ी में मेरी संवेदनाएं उनके परिजनों और प्रशंसकों के साथ हैं। ओम शांति!

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Spoke to @VP Kamala Harris a short while ago. I deeply appreciate the assurance of vaccine supplies to India as part of the US Strategy for Global Vaccine Sharing. I also thanked her for the all the support and solidarity from the US government, businesses and Indian diaspora.

description: Prime Minister of India

description: Prime Minister of India
text:
आज रामनवमी है और मर्यादा पुरुषोत्तम श्रीराम का हम सभी को यही संदेश है कि मर्यादाओं का पालन करें।
 
कोरोना के इस संकट काल में, कोरोना से बचने के जो भी उपाय हैं, कृपया करके उनका पालन कीजिए।
 
'दवाई भी, कड़ाई भी' के मंत्र को याद रखिए।

description: Prime Minister of India

description: Prime Minister of India

description: Prime Minister of India

description: Prime Minister of India

description: Prime Minister of India

You would love visiting the Nature Park. It houses a Mist Garden, Chess Garden, Selfie Points, Sculpture Park and an outdoor maze.

I specially call upon parents to take their children here. https://t.co/y7ATOsarr3

description: Prime Minister of India
text: On the auspicious occasion of Ashadhi Ekadashi, my greetings to everyone. On this special day, we pray to Lord Vitthal to bless us with abundance of happiness and good health. The Varkari movement represents the finest of our traditions and emphasises on harmony and equality.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: On Tagore Jayanti, I bow to the great Gurudev Tagore. May his exemplary ideals keep giving us strength and inspiration to build the India he dreamt of.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Anguished by the passing away of my friend from Parliament, Shri Rajeev Satav Ji. He was an upcoming leader with much potential. Condolences to his family, friends and supporters. Om Shanti.

description: Prime Minister of India

description: Prime Minister of India

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Elections are taking place in Assam, Kerala, Puducherry, Tamil Nadu and West Bengal. I request the people in these places to vote in record numbers, particularly the young voters.

text:
Very good initiative!  @myogiadityanath

भारत रत्न डॉ. बाबासाहेब अम्बेडकर को उनकी जयंती पर शत-शत नमन। समाज के वंचित वर्गों को मुख्यधारा में लाने के लिए किया गया उनका संघर्ष हर पीढ़ी के लिए एक मिसाल बना रहेगा।

I bow to the great Dr. Babasaheb Ambedkar on #AmbedkarJayanti.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: I bow to Dr. Syama Prasad Mookerjee on his Jayanti. His lofty ideals motivate millions across our nation. Dr. Mookerjee devoted his life towards India’s unity and progress. He also distinguished himself as a remarkable scholar and intellectual.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Pained by the loss of lives due to a fire at a factory in Pune, Maharashtra. Condolences to the bereaved families.

description: Prime Minister of India
text:
Best wishes on the auspicious occasion of Eid-ul-Fitr. Praying for everyone’s good health and well-being. Powered by our collective efforts, may we overcome the global pandemic and work towards furthering human welfare. 

Eid Mubarak!

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Jagmohan Ji’s demise is a monumental loss for our nation. He was an exemplary administrator and a renowned scholar. He always worked towards the betterment of India. His ministerial tenure was marked by innovative policy making. Condolences to his family and admirers. Om Shanti.

description: Prime Minister of India

description: Prime Minister of India

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Birthday greetings to Shri @AshwiniVaishnaw. He is working to transform key infrastructure related sectors of governance, which would benefit several of our citizens. Praying for his long and healthy life.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: I would like to thank the people of Bangladesh for their affection during my visit. I would also like to thank PM Sheikh Hasina and the Bangladesh Government for the warm hospitality. I am sure this visit will lead to further strengthening of bilateral ties between our nations.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Best wishes to our senior Cabinet colleague Shri @rajnathsingh Ji on his birthday. He is admired across the spectrum for his warm personality and wisdom. He is an outstanding Parliamentarian and administrator. Praying for his long and healthy life in service of our nation.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Congratulations to Shri @vijayanpinarayi Ji on taking oath as CM and commencing his second term in office.

description: Prime Minister of India

description: Prime Minister of India

description: Prime Minister of India

description: Prime Minister of India
text: My valued colleague @sarbanandsonwal Ji was at the helm of a pro-people and pro-development administration over the last five years. His contribution towards Assam’s progress and strengthening the party in the state is immense.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Had a good conversation with His Highness @TamimBinHamad, Amir of Qatar today. I thanked His Highness for the solidarity and offer of support in India's fight against COVID-19. I also conveyed our gratitude for the care being provided to the Indian community in Qatar.

text: Reviewed preparedness to handle the ongoing COVID-19 situation. Aspects relating to medicines, oxygen, ventilators and vaccination were discussed. Like we did last year, we will successfully fight COVID with even greater speed and coordination. https://t.co/cxhTxLtxJa

description: Prime Minister of India
text: The people of West Bengal are voting to elect a new assembly. On the sixth phase today, urging those whose seats are polling to exercise their franchise.

text: स्वतंत्रता सेनानी और सामाजिक न्याय के प्रबल पैरोकार बाबू जगजीवन राम को उनकी जयंती पर विनम्र श्रद्धांजलि। समाज के शोषितों और वंचितों के उत्थान के लिए उनके प्रभावी प्रयास सदैव प्रेरणास्रोत रहेंगे।

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Discussed the pandemic situation with my friend Lyonchhen @PMBhutan, and conveyed appreciation for the solidarity and prayers expressed by the leaders and people of Bhutan. The India-Bhutan friendship is truly special, and we will continue to fight this crisis together.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Greetings to all Chartered Accountants on CA Day. This community has a vital role in India’s progress. I call upon all CAs to keep the focus on excellence so that Indian firms emerge as one of the best globally.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Discussed the COVID-19 situation with Chief Ministers of the states seeing a surge in infections. We discussed the steps being taken to strengthen the fight against the pandemic. https://t.co/vE3UAHXmMr

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Saddened by the demise of Dr. Guruprasad Mohapatra, DPIIT Secretary. I had worked with him extensively in Gujarat and at the Centre. He had a great understanding of administrative issues and was known for his innovative zeal. Condolences to his family and friends. Om Shanti.

description: Prime Minister of India
text:
Greetings on Easter! 

On this day, we remember the pious teachings of Jesus Christ. His emphasis on social empowerment inspires millions across the world.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: भाजपा के वरिष्ठ नेता और पूर्व केंद्रीय राज्य मंत्री बची सिंह रावत जी के निधन से बहुत दुख पहुंचा है। उनका पूरा जीवन जनहित और देशहित में समर्पित रहा। शोक की इस घड़ी में उनके परिजनों और शुभचिंतकों के प्रति मैं अपनी गहरी संवेदना व्यक्त करता हूं। ओम शांति!

description: Prime Minister of India
text: हिमाचल दिवस के अवसर पर राज्य के सभी निवासियों को ढेर सारी शुभकामनाएं। अपनी संस्कृति और परंपरा को संजोने के साथ-साथ यहां के लोगों ने अपने अथक परिश्रम के बल पर राज्य को नई ऊंचाइयां प्रदान की हैं। मेरी कामना है कि यह प्रदेश देश की प्रगति में यूं ही अपना योगदान देता रहे।

description: Prime Minister of India
text: उत्तराखंड के मुख्यमंत्री तीरथ सिंह रावत जी को जन्मदिन की ढेरों शुभकामनाएं। ईश्वर उन्हें स्वस्थ और सुदीर्घ जीवन प्रदान करे। @TIRATHSRAWAT

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Our democracy’s biggest strength is the ability to sit across a table and exchange views. I told the leaders of J&K that it is the people, specially the youth who have to provide political leadership to J&K, and ensure their aspirations are duly fulfilled. https://t.co/t743b0Su4L

description: Prime Minister of India
text: महान समाजसेवी, विचारक, दार्शनिक एवं लेखक महात्मा ज्योतिबा फुले की जयंती पर उन्हें कोटि-कोटि नमन। वे जीवनपर्यंत महिलाओं की शिक्षा और उनके सशक्तिकरण के लिए प्रतिबद्ध रहे। समाज सुधार के प्रति उनकी निष्ठा आने वाली पीढ़ियों को प्रेरित करती रहेगी।

description: Prime Minister of India
text: My discussion with @POTUS @JoeBiden also underscored the importance of smooth and efficient supply chains of vaccine raw materials and medicines. India-US healthcare partnership can address the global challenge of COVID-19.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Reviewed the work being done by the armed forces in combatting COVID-19, including the efforts to enhance medical capacities and utilising human resources. https://t.co/WFd8n2hyuy

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Spoke to PM @sugawitter of Japan on phone. We reviewed the progress in various ongoing bilateral initiatives. We also discussed our cooperation in diverse areas including high technology, skill development and in fighting the COVID-19 pandemic together.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Met a delegation of MLAs from Puducherry. Discussed the various efforts for Puducherry's all-round development. https://t.co/sK4fUMOR3E

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Received the first copy of the book, ‘The Ramayana of Shri Guru Gobind Singh Ji’ penned by Late Mrs. Baljit Kaur Tulsi Ji, who is the mother of noted lawyer Shri KTS Tulsi Ji. The book has been published by IGNCA. https://t.co/ZKdWJjcble

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Spoke to former PM Shri @H_D_Devegowda Ji and enquired about his and his wife’s health. Praying for their quick recovery.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: This is how Congress trampled over our democratic ethos. We remember all those greats who resisted the Emergency and protected Indian democracy. #DarkDaysOfEmergency https://t.co/PxQwYG5w1w

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Had a productive Virtual Summit with my friend UK PM @BorisJohnson. We adopted an ambitious Roadmap 2030 for elevating India-UK ties to a Comprehensive Strategic Partnership.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Thank you Goa for the continuous support to BJP. The results of the Municipal Elections 2021 show the people’s appreciation towards our Party’s development agenda. I laud all hardworking BJP Karyakartas who went among people and worked hard during the campaign.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Today’s meeting with political leaders from Jammu and Kashmir is an important step in the ongoing efforts towards a developed and progressive J&K, where all-round growth is furthered. https://t.co/SjwvSv3HIp

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Dr. Srikumar Banerjee will be remembered for his pioneering contributions to Indian science, especially in the areas of atomic energy and metallurgy. He was also an outstanding mentor and institution builder. Saddened by his passing away. Condolences to his family. Om Shanti.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Ex-gratia of Rs. 2 lakh would be given to the next of kin of those who lost their lives due to Cyclone Tauktae in all the affected states. Rs. 50,000 would be given to the injured. GOI is in full solidarity with those affected and will provide them all possible support.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: My best wishes to President Alberto Fernández of Argentina for a quick recovery from COVID-19. @alferdez

description: Prime Minister of India
text: आजादी के क्रांतिदूत अमर शहीद वीर भगत सिंह, सुखदेव और राजगुरु को शहीदी दिवस पर शत-शत नमन। मां भारती के इन महान सपूतों का बलिदान देश की हर पीढ़ी के लिए प्रेरणास्रोत बना रहेगा। जय हिंद! #ShaheedDiwas https://t.co/qs3SqAHkO9

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Took stock of the usage of gaseous oxygen produced by industry, for medical purposes, with adjacent temporary hospitals. https://t.co/puuRr1BaBG

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Passing away of Shri Sunderlal Bahuguna Ji is a monumental loss for our nation. He manifested our centuries old ethos of living in harmony with nature. His simplicity and spirit of compassion will never be forgotten. My thoughts are with his family and many admirers. Om Shanti.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Reviewed different aspects relating to the COVID-19 situation. This includes different sources of oxygen availability and the supply of medicines across the nation. https://t.co/fq164BKXr7

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Countless people across India are praying for the speedy recovery of Kalyan Singh Ji. Yesterday @JPNadda Ji, CM @myogiadityanath Ji and others went to the hospital to meet him. I just spoke to his grandson and enquired about his health.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: The situation in Himachal Pradesh due to heavy rains is being closely monitored. Authorities are working with the State Government. All possible support is being extended. I pray for the safety of those in affected areas.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: On the special occasion of Basava Jayanthi, I bow to Jagadguru Basaveshwara. His noble teachings, particularly the emphasis on social empowerment, harmony, brotherhood and compassion continue to inspire several people.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Our partnership with Bangladesh is an important pillar of our Neighbourhood First policy, and we are committed to further deepen and diversify it. We will continue to support Bangladesh's remarkable development journey, under Prime Minister Sheikh Hasina's dynamic leadership

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Family Pension under ESIC and EPFO- Employees’ Deposit Linked Insurance Scheme will provide a financial cushion to those families who have lost their earning member due to COVID-19. GOI stands in solidarity with these families. https://t.co/ppfmf5Q66y

description: Prime Minister of India
text: At 11 AM tomorrow, 5th June will take part in the World Environment Programme on the theme of ‘promotion of biofuels for better environment.’ Would also interact with farmers to hear their experiences of using ethanol and biogas. https://t.co/1BzJRWgivs

description: Prime Minister of India
text: I had spoken to Shri Milkha Singh Ji just a few days ago. Little did I know that it would be our last conversation. Several budding athletes will derive strength from his life journey. My condolences to his family and many admirers all over the world.

description: Prime Minister of India
text:
On the special occasion of his 400th Parkash Purab, I bow to Sri Guru Teg Bahadur Ji.
He is widely respected globally for his courage and his efforts to serve the downtrodden. He refused to bow to tyranny and injustice. His supreme sacrifice gives strength and motivation to many.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: 'Jal', 'Thal' and 'Nabh'...our armed forces have left no stone unturned in strengthening the fight against COVID-19. https://t.co/JOcRRrhJgR

description: Prime Minister of India
text:
Good to see our healthcare workers and nurses set an example in reducing vaccine wastage. 

Reducing vaccine wastage is important in strengthening the fight against COVID-19. https://t.co/xod0lomGDb

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Warm felicitations and greetings to @POTUS @JoeBiden  and the people of the USA on their 245th Independence Day. As vibrant democracies, India and USA share values of freedom and liberty. Our strategic partnership has a truly global significance.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Padma Vibhushan Sir Anerood Jugnauth, a tall leader & statesman, was the architect of modern Mauritius. A proud Pravasi Bharatiya, he helped forge the special bilateral relationship that will benefit from his legacy. Condolences to his family & the people of Mauritius. Om Shanti. https://t.co/CktEnK4XMn

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Reviewed the efforts being taken by the Indian Army in the fight against COVID-19. https://t.co/bulevS6Kvu

description: Prime Minister of India

description: Prime Minister of India
text: The people of Assam have again blessed the NDA’s development agenda and the pro-people track record of our Government in the state. I thank the people of Assam for the blessings. I appreciate the hard work of NDA Karyakartas and their untiring efforts in serving the people.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Taking forward the commitment to transform India-EU relationship for global good, I had a virtual interaction with all leaders of EU Member States and Presidents @CharlesMichel @eucopresident and @vonderleyen for India-EU Leaders' Meeting.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Shri Yashpal Sharma Ji was a much beloved member of the Indian cricket team, including the legendary 1983 squad. He was an inspiration for teammates, fans as well as budding cricketers. Anguished by his passing away. Condolences to his family and admirers. Om Shanti.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Saddened by the demise of MP Shri Raghunath Mohapatra Ji. He made pioneering contributions to the world of art, architecture and culture. He will be remembered for his contributions towards popularising traditional crafts. My thoughts are with his family and admirers. Om Shanti.

description: Prime Minister of India
text:
Happy to have met you and the brilliant Nambi Narayanan Ji. This film covers an important topic, which more people must know about. 

Our scientists and technicians have made great sacrifices for our country, glimpses of which I could see in the clips of Rocketry. https://t.co/GDopym5rTm

description: Prime Minister of India
text: During today’s high level meet, we reviewed the situation relating to oxygen supply and ways to further boost oxygen availability in the coming days. https://t.co/ohHZEHotUe

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Saddened by the demise of His Grace The Most Rev. Dr. Philipose Mar Chrysostom Mar Thoma Valiya Metropolitan. He will be remembered for his rich theological knowledge and many efforts to remove human suffering. Condolences to the members of the Malankara Mar Thoma Syrian Church.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: A New Year and a resolve for new beginnings and progress for the great land of West Bengal! https://t.co/JYpwx6SxAy

description: Prime Minister of India
text: Tomorrow, 25th March is special for Jammu and Kashmir. A majestic tulip garden on the foothills of the Zabarwan Mountains will open for visitors. The Garden will see over 15 lakh flowers of more than 64 varieties in bloom. https://t.co/LwRPglZ1jO

description: Prime Minister of India
text: My thoughts are with the British people and the Royal Family on the passing away of HRH The Prince Philip, Duke of Edinburgh. He had a distinguished career in the military and was at the forefront of many community service initiatives. May his soul rest in peace.

description: Prime Minister of India
text: At around 8:30 AM tomorrow, 24th July, will be sharing my message at the Ashadha Purnima-Dhamma Chakra Day programme.

description: Prime Minister of India

description: Prime Minister of India

अब जरूरत है कि देश में ऐसे Products बनें जो Made in India हों, Made for the World हों।

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text:
मैं आज देश के किसानों को स्पष्ट संदेश देना चाहता हूं। आप किसी भी तरह के भ्रम में मत पड़िए। 

इन लोगों से देश के किसानों को सतर्क रहना है। 

ऐसे लोगों से सावधान रहें जिन्होंने दशकों तक देश पर राज किया और जो आज किसानों से झूठ बोल रहे हैं: PM

बीते कुछ समय से जो कष्ट देशवासियो ने सहा है,अनेको लोग जिस दर्द से गुजरे है, तकलीफ से गुजरे है वो मैं भी उतना ही महसूस कर रहा हूं: PM

text:
आज देश में 130 करोड़ लोगों के पास आधार कार्ड, 41 करोड़ से ज्यादा देशवासियों के पास जनधन खाते हैं।

इनमें से करीब 55% जनधन खाते महिलाओं के हैं और इनमें करीब डेढ़ लाख करोड़ रुपए जमा हैं: PM

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text: Due to lockdown, many initiatives taken by the Government and a people driven fight, India is much better placed than many other nations.  India's recovery rate is rising: PM @narendramodi

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text:
अपने बाल मित्रों से एक बात विशेष तौर पर कहना चाहता हूं।

मेरे बाल मित्र, घर में ऐसा माहौल बनाएं कि बिना काम, बिना कारण घर के लोग, घर से बाहर न निकलें।

आपकी जिद बहुत बड़ा परिणाम ला सकती है: PM @narendramodi

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text:
जो लोग भी वैक्सीन को लेकर आशंका पैदा कर रहे हैं, अफवाहें फैला रहे हैं, वो भोले-भाले भाई-बहनों के जीवन के साथ बहुत बड़ा खिलवाड़ कर रहे हैं।

ऐसी अफवाहों से सतर्क रहने की जरूरत है: PM @narendramodi

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text: मांगने के लिए मजबूर करने वाली सोच लोकतंत्र की सोच नहीं हो सकती है: PM @narendramodi

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text:
मेरा स्पष्ट मानना है:
 
The future of a nation is what its youth think today. 

Your dreams are going to shape the reality of India.

इसलिए, ये time future ready होने का है, ये time अभी से future fit होने का है: PM

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text: त्योहारों का ये समय, जरूरतें भी बढ़ाता है, खर्चे भी बढ़ाता है। इन सभी बातों को ध्यान में रखते हुए ये फैसला लिया गया है कि प्रधानमंत्री गरीब कल्याण अन्न योजना का विस्तार अब दीवाली और छठ पूजा तक, यानि नवंबर महीने के आखिर तक कर दिया जाए: PM @narendramodi

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text: गंगा का जल निर्मल होगा: मोदी। https://t.co/YP35CZDRuv

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text:
आप भगवान राम की अद्भुत शक्ति देखिए।

इमारतें नष्ट कर दी गईं, अस्तित्व मिटाने का प्रयास भी बहुत हुआ, 

लेकिन राम आज भी हमारे मन में बसे हैं, हमारी संस्कृति का आधार हैं: PM

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text:
हमें इस बात का हमेशा ध्यान रखना है कि हम कोरोना को जितना रोक पाएंगे, उसका बढ़ना जितना रोक पाएंगे, 

उतना ही हमारी अर्थव्यवस्था खुलेगी, हमारे दफ्तर खुलेंगे, मार्केट खुलेंगे, ट्रांसपोर्ट के साधन खुलेंगे, और उतने ही रोजगार के नए अवसर भी बनेंगे: PM

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text:
Active cases
का प्रतिशत कम हुआ है,
recovery rate बढ़ा है,
 
तो इसका अर्थ है कि हमारे प्रयास कारगर सिद्ध हो रहे हैं!
 
सबसे अहम बात है,
कि इससे लोगों के बीच भी एक भरोसा बढ़ा है,
आत्मविश्वास बढ़ा है,
और डर भी कुछ कम हुआ है: PM @narendramodi

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text: गरीब लोगों के लिए छह साल में सबसे अधिक काम हुआ। https://t.co/QZqgwW7JXl

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text: Saddened by the building collapse in Mahad, Raigad in Maharashtra. My thoughts are with the families of those who lost their dear ones. I pray the injured recover soon. Local authorities and NDRF teams are at the site of the tragedy, providing all possible assistance: PM

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text: Rajya Sabha MP Shri Sharad Pawar met PM @narendramodi. @PawarSpeaks https://t.co/INj26CLl0k

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text: इस सर्वदलीय बैठक के माध्यम से मैं शहीदो के परिवारों को भी ये विश्वास दिलाता हूं की पूरा देश उनके साथ है, पूरा देश उन्हें नमन करता है: PM @narendramodi

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text:
योग का अर्थ ही है- ‘समत्वम् योग उच्यते’
अर्थात, अनुकूलता-प्रतिकूलता, सफलता-विफलता, सुख-संकट, हर परिस्थिति में समान रहने, अडिग रहने का नाम ही योग है: PM @narendramodi

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text:
जो 1-2 दिन के लोकल लॉकडाउन होते हैं, वो कोरोना को रोकने में कितना प्रभावी हैं, हर राज्य को इसका अवलोकन करना चाहिए।

कहीं ऐसा तो नहीं कि इस वजह से आपके राज्य में आर्थिक गतिविधियां शुरू होने में दिक्कत हो रही है?

मेरा आग्रह है कि सभी राज्य इस बारे में गंभीरता से सोचें: PM

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text:
इस वायरस के खिलाफ हमारे हथियार क्या हैं?

हमारे हथियार हैं- Local containment zones, aggressive testing और लोगों तक सही और पूरी जानकारी: PM @narendramodi

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text:
इस साल कोरोना संक्रमण के दौरान भी रबी सीज़न में किसानों से गेहूं की रिकॉर्ड खरीद की गई है।

इस साल रबी में गेहूं, धान, दलहन और तिलहन को मिलाकर, किसानों को 1 लाख 13 हजार करोड़ रुपए MSP पर दिया गया है।

ये राशि भी पिछले साल के मुकाबले 30 प्रतिशत से ज्यादा है: PM

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text: हाल ही में हमारी सेनाओं ने निर्णय लिया है कि वो 100 से ज्यादा हथियारों और साजो-सामान को विदेश से नहीं मंगवाएगी: PM @narendramodi

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text: बीते वर्षों में देश corruption पर zero tolerance की approach के साथ आगे बढ़ा है: PM

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text:
आज जब केंद्र सरकार, किसानों को उनके अधिकार दे रही है, तो भी ये लोग विरोध पर उतर आए हैं।

ये लोग चाहते हैं कि देश का किसान खुले बाजार में अपनी उपज नहीं बेच पाए।

जिन सामानों की, उपकरणों की किसान पूजा करता है, उन्हें आग लगाकर ये  लोग अब किसानों को अपमानित कर रहे हैं: PM

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text:
आज़ादी के इतने वर्षों के बाद भी साल 2014 से पहले तक देश में 16 IITs थीं। 

बीते 6 साल में औसतन हर साल एक नई IIT खोली गई है। इसमें से एक कर्नाटका के धारवाड़ में भी खुली है।

2014 तक भारत में 9 IIITs थीं। इसके बाद के 5 सालों में 16 IIITs बनाई गई हैं: PM

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text: Shri Girish Chandra Murmu, Comptroller and Auditor General of India called on PM @narendramodi. https://t.co/So5Z8CFtJv

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text: टीका उत्सव पर देशवासियों से आग्रह। https://t.co/GvGV3OCnP7

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text: हमारे students में, हमारे युवाओं में Critical और Innovative ability विकसित कैसे हो सकती है, जबतक हमारी शिक्षा में Passion ना हो, Philosophy of Education ना हो, Purpose of Education ना हो: PM @narendramodi

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text: Tomorrow, PM @narendramodi will embark on a 3 city visit to personally review the vaccine development & manufacturing process. He will visit the Zydus Biotech Park in Ahmedabad, Bharat Biotech in Hyderabad & Serum Institute of India in Pune.

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text: We need to work together to ensure a timely roll-out of 5G to leapfrog into the future and empower millions of Indians: PM

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text:
The Gita makes us think.

It inspires us to question.

It encourages debate.

The Gita keeps our mind open: PM @narendramodi

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text:
Buddhism teaches respect.
 
Respect for people.
 
Respect for the poor.
 
Respect for women.
 
Respect for peace and
non-violence.
 
Therefore, the teachings of Buddhism are the means to a sustainable planet: PM @narendramodi

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text:
मैं देश के प्रत्येक किसान को इस बात का भरोसा देता हूं कि MSP की व्यवस्था जैसे पहले चली आ रही थी, वैसे ही चलती रहेगी। 

इसी तरह हर सीजन में सरकारी खरीद के लिए जिस तरह अभियान चलाया जाता है, वो भी पहले की तरह चलते रहेंगे: PM

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text:
आज भारत में 80 करोड़ से ज्यादा लोगों को मुफ्त राशन दिया जा रहा है। इसका बहुत बड़ा लाभ बनारस के भी गरीबों को, श्रमिकों को हो रहा है।
आप कल्पना कर सकते हैं कि भारत, अमेरिका से भी दोगुनी आबादी से, एक पैसा लिए बिना उनका भरण-पोषण कर रहा है: PM @narendramodi

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text:
इस वर्ष के बजट पर जिस तरह का positive response आया है, उसने जता दिया है कि mood of the nation क्या है। 

देश मन बना चुका है। 

देश तेजी से आगे बढ़ना चाहता है, देश अब समय नहीं गंवाना चाहता है: PM @narendramodi

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text:
जो टैक्स देने में सक्षम हैं, लेकिन अभी वो टैक्स नेट में नहीं है, वो स्वप्रेरणा से आगे आएं, ये मेरा आग्रह है और उम्मीद भी।

आइए, विश्वास के, अधिकारों के, दायित्वों के, प्लेटफॉर्म की भावना का सम्मान करते हुए, नए भारत, आत्मनिर्भर भारत के संकल्प को सिद्ध करें: PM @narendramodi

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text: कृषि सुधारों से आगे बढ़ रहा है देश। https://t.co/jlxJJDw0mr

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text: मैं बहुत गर्व से कहूंगा कि सिर्फ 3 महीने के भीतर ही Personal Protective Equipment -PPE की सैकड़ों करोड़ की इंडस्ट्री आपने ही खड़ी की है: PM @narendramodi

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text: पूर्वी लद्दाख में जो हुआ, इसको लेकर आपने रक्षा मंत्री जी और विदेश मंत्री जी को सुना भी और Presentation को भी देखा । न वहां कोई हमारी सीमा में घुस आया है और न ही कोई घुसा हुआ है, न ही हमारी कोई पोस्ट किसी दूसरे के कब्जे में है: PM @narendramodi

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text:
ड्राइविंग लाइसेंस हो, बर्थ सर्टिफिकेट हो, बिजली का बिल भरना हो, पानी का बिल भरना हो, इनकम टैक्स रिटर्न भरना हो, इस तरह के अनेक कामों के लिए अब प्रक्रियाएं डिजिटल इंडिया की मदद से बहुत आसान, बहुत तेज हुई है।

और गांवों में तो ये सब, अब अपने घर के पास CSC सेंटर में भी हो रहा है: PM

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text:
May the thoughts of Lord Buddha further brightness, togetherness and brotherhood.
 
May his blessings inspire us to do good: PM @narendramodi

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text:
आज सिर्फ अटल जी का ही सपना नहीं पूरा हुआ है, 

आज हिमाचल प्रदेश के करोड़ों लोगों का भी दशकों पुराना इंतजार खत्म हुआ है: PM

#AtalTunnel

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text:
आज भारत वो सब कर रहा है, जिसकी कुछ साल पहले तक कल्पना नहीं होती थी।

आज़ादी के 75 साल जब देश मनाएगा, तो देश उन लक्ष्यों की ओर आगे बढ़ेगा, उन्हें प्राप्त करने के लिए मजबूत कदम उठाएगा, जो कभी असंभव लगते थे: PM @narendramodi

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text:
देश ने ये तय किया है कि अब हर साल हम नेताजी की जयंती, यानी 23 जनवरी को ‘पराक्रम दिवस’ के रूप में मनाया करेंगे।

हमारे नेताजी भारत के पराक्रम की प्रतिमूर्ति भी हैं और प्रेरणा भी हैं: PM

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text: मुझे उम्मीद है, हमारे आज के प्रयास, इस दशक में अंडमान-निकोबार को, वहां के लोगों को, न सिर्फ नई सहूलियत देंगे बल्कि वर्ल्ड टूरिस्ट मैप में भी प्रमुख स्थान के तौर पर स्थापित करेंगे: PM @narendramodi

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text:
आज पूरे विश्व समुदाय के सामने एक बहुत बड़ा सवाल है कि जिस संस्था का गठन तब की परिस्थितियों में हुआ था, 

उसका स्वरूप क्या आज भी प्रासंगिक है?: PM

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text:
एक टेस्ट, एक मार्क्सशीट क्या बच्चों के सीखने की, उनके मानसिक विकास की Parameter हो सकती है?

आज सच्चाई ये है कि मार्क्सशीट, मानसिक प्रैशरशीट बन गई है: PM 
#ShikshakParv

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text: PM @narendramodi has approved an ex-gratia of Rs. 2 lakh each from PMNRF for the next of kin of those who have lost their lives due to the tragic avalanche caused by a Glacier breach in Chamoli, Uttrakhand. Rs. 50,000 would be given to those seriously injured.

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text: दीपावली तक 80 करोड़ लोगों को मुफ्त अनाज। https://t.co/hzvZlUREQU

text: Our motto is 'Sabka Saath,  Sabka Vikaas,  Sabka Vishwas'  - meaning 'Together, for everyone's growth,  with everyone's trust'. This resonates with the core SDG principle of  leaving no one behind: PM @narendramodi

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text:
हमें ये हमेशा याद रखना है कि हम सभी के लिए सर्वोच्च हित- देशहित है।

जब हम सबका हित सोचेंगे, तभी हमारी भी प्रगति होगी, उन्नति होगी: PM

description: Office of the Prime Minister of India
text:
आज यूपी में कानून का राज है।

माफियाराज और आतंकवाद, जो कभी बेकाबू हो रहे थे, उन पर अब कानून का शिकंजा है।
